logs/
*.lock
# ...but the dependency lock IS committed (reproducible installs).
!uv.lock

# Internal session notes (not for public repo)
session-notes.md
doc-updates.md
doc-updates-v3.md

# Local run outputs — contain REAL tenant data (user emails, workspace/model
